-------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------




for external service and assign the service an external IP address we use this Type


type: LoadBalancer

nodePort: 30000

(30000 - 32767)





Default Type = ClusterIP     (Only Internal IP Address)


